node.text: They say kings are the most important chess piece, but, nah, it’s actually the pawn. Here’s the proof from The Queen’s Gambit. Happy International Chess Day! ♟️❤️

Never Have I Ever S2 arrives July 15th.

node.text: it's been two years since Love is Blind changed the dating game forever and everyone from Season 1 — yes, even Jessica! — is coming back for After the Altar, a three-episode reunion series that will heal old wounds and maybe create some new ones...premieres July 28

node.title: Love is Blind: After the Altar | Trailer

Fate: The Winx Saga Season 2 is officially in production!

The returning cast gathered to meet new cast members Brandon Grace as Grey, Éanna Hardwicke as Sebastian and ... Paulina Chávez as Flora!!!
